{
  "stem": "6526.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And tailoring in France was the main profession.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And not just a tailor, he was a good tailor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so we decided not to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that's how we remained in Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there were many.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were no-- the only thing urging to leave was the Zionist organization.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a Zionist organization, [INAUDIBLE] Zionist.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, mostly all the people like my father and other ones belonged to.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was younger ones and still younger ones.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were the-- the-- [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was, let's say, socialist minded.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All these were urging to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "At that time, we could not go to Israel because of Palestine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But how could we go when the-- it was, as we can say, it was occupied by the British, by English.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had to give you a permit to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People used to apply.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It took three, four, five years to get it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then there was the [POLISH], right [POLISH] and left [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All those--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--Zionist minded.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then there was the Bund, which was socialist minded.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they say they don't go any place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We've got to make a socialist country in Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then there was the Communist Party, which was underground, which was not allowed to be.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But nevertheless, there were many Jews that belonged to the Communist Party.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And although we were Zionist minded-- especially my-- as my brother, my brother belongs to-- but had friends that were Communists.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when it came before the May 1, they-- they-- they used to throw in a flag on the electric wires to show that the Communists still exist.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they used to hide-- my brother used to hide his friends' flags.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When it comes the 1st, we'll be able to take it.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
